headline: Garmin revolutionizes aviation charting with SmartCharts
summary: Garmin (NYSE: GRMN) today announced SmartCharts, a dynamic aviation charting solution that will provide pilots with a simplified and intuitive experience by producing clear and relevant data to depict a chart tailored for their specific flight operation.
